Class SmartsQueryVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openscience.cdk.smiles.smarts.parser.SmartsQueryVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SMARTSParserVisitor
    @Deprecated
public class SmartsQueryVisitor
extends Object
implements SMARTSParserVisitor
    Deprecated.
    An AST tree visitor. It builds an instance of QueryAtomContainer from the AST tree. To use this visitor: 
     SMARTSParser parser = new SMARTSParser(new java.io.StringReader("C*C"));
 ASTStart ast = parser.start();
 SmartsQueryVisitor visitor = new SmartsQueryVisitor();
 QueryAtomContainer query = visitor.visit(ast, null);
    Author:
    Dazhi Jiao
